<h2>About</h2>
<p>The Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS) is a streamlined platform designed to facilitate the submission, review, and approval of monthly claims for Independent Contractor (IC) lecturers. Our goal is to simplify the administrative processes and ensure a transparent and efficient workflow for both lecturers and academic staff.</p>

<h3>Key Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Claim Submission:</strong> Independent Contractor lecturers can easily submit their monthly claims for the work they've completed, along with any necessary supporting documentation such as timesheets and receipts.</li>
    <li><strong>Approval Workflow:</strong> Programme Coordinators and Academic Managers have dedicated roles within the system to verify, review, and approve submitted claims, ensuring accountability at each step.</li>
    <li><strong>Status Tracking:</strong> Lecturers can monitor the status of their claims in real time, from submission to approval and payment processing, ensuring transparency in the workflow.</li>
    <li><strong>Document Management:</strong> CMCS provides a secure, centralized location to store all claim-related documents, making it easy to access past claims, receipts, and approvals when needed.</li>
    <li><strong>Automated Notifications:</strong> Users are notified of key events such as claim approval or rejection, requests for additional documentation, or when payments have been processed.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Benefits of CMCS</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Time-saving:</strong> The system eliminates the need for manual paperwork and back-and-forth emails, making claim processing much faster.</li>
    <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Both lecturers and academic staff can track claims at any stage of the approval process, ensuring clarity and reducing disputes.</li>
    <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> CMCS is accessible from anywhere, allowing lecturers to submit claims remotely, and Programme Coordinators or Academic Managers to approve claims from their devices.</li>
    <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> The system ensures that all claims follow the institution’s policies and guidelines, reducing the risk of errors and ensuring proper documentation is maintained.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Why Choose CMCS?</h3>
<p>CMCS was specifically designed to address the needs of educational institutions and Independent Contractors, ensuring that the claims process is both efficient and transparent. By using CMCS, institutions can minimize administrative overhead, reduce processing times, and create a more organized and accountable system for claims management.</p>

